    "body": "#### vim-patch:ff7fcb8: runtime(pfmain): Add smtp_destination_rate_delay to syntax script\n\ncloses: vim/vim#20505\n\nhttps://github.com/vim/vim/commit/ff7fcb8f012230f3cbb28d281f5f069390be1e1f\n\nCo-authored-by: Leo Feyer <1192057+leofeyer@users.noreply.github.com>\n\n\n#### vim-patch:1fee3cd: runtime(beancount): Include Beancount runtime files\n\nInclude with adjustments from the upstream repo:\nhttps://github.com/nathangrigg/vim-beancount\n\ncloses: vim/vim#20373\n\nhttps://github.com/vim/vim/commit/1fee3cd4b9a38b18656933d38a4977548d27808b\n\nCo-authored-by: Bruno BELANYI <bruno@belanyi.fr>",
    "closed_at": "2026-06-14T02:02:39Z",
